     Rhein shall be entitled, to the extent permitted under any applicable law, to select and change a beneficiary or beneficiaries to receive any compensation or benefits payable hereunder following Rhein's death by giving the Company written notice thereof. In the absence of such a selection, any compensation or benefit payable under this Agreement following the death of Rhein shall be payable to Rhein's spouse, or if such spouse shall not survive Rhein, to Rhein's estate. In the event of Rhein's death or a judicial determination of Rhein's incompetence, reference in this Agreement to Rhein shall be deemed, where appropriate, to refer to Rhein's beneficiary, estate or other legal representative.
