Employee and Related Matters
          (a) . Sellers shall terminate the employment of the Transferred Employees, other than those Transferred Employees set forth on , effective as of the Closing or such later time as such individual becomes a Transferred Employee under Section 8.2.2(b) (as applicable, the "Effective Time").
