The Buyers
 
  Arrow Electronics, Inc., a New York corporation, is a major global provider of products, services and solutions to industrial and commercial users of electronic components and computer products. Headquartered in Melville, New York, Arrow serves as a supply channel partner for nearly 600 suppliers and more than 130,000 original equipment manufacturers, contract manufacturers and commercial customers through a global network of over 270 locations in 53 countries and territories. Arrow Electronics Canada Ltd, a Canadian corporation and Support Net, Inc., an Indiana corporation, are wholly-owned subsidiaries of Arrow.
