About Agilysys, Inc.
Agilysys, Inc. (NASDAQ: AGYS) is a leading provider of innovative IT solutions to the corporate and public sectors, with special expertise in select vertical markets, including retail and hospitality. The company uses technology  including hardware, software and services  to help customers resolve their most complicated IT needs. The company possesses expertise in enterprise architecture and high availability, infrastructure optimization, storage and resource management, and business continuity; and provides industry-specific software, services and expertise to the retail and hospitality markets. Headquartered in Boca Raton, Fla., Agilysys operates extensively throughout North America, with additional sales offices in the United Kingdom and China. For more information, visit .
