Item 2.02 Results of Operations and Financial Condition; and
Item 7.01 Regulation FD Disclosure
On August 2, 2007 Agilysys, Inc. (the "Company") issued a press release announcing its results for the fiscal 2008 first quarter ended June 30, 2007. A copy of the press release is attached hereto as Exhibit 99.1 and incorporated by reference herein.
Item 9.01 Financial Statements and Exhibits
(c) Exhibits
