Item 8.01  Other Events.
On August 2, 2007 Agilysys, Inc. (the "Company") issued a press release and conducted a conference call, both of which reported the Company's results for the fiscal 2008 first quarter ended June 30, 2007. The press release was filed with the Securities and Exchange Commission on Form 8-K dated August 2, 2007. During the conference call, management discussed the Company's previously announced intention to conduct a self-tender offer. Following are the related excerpts from the conference call that discussed the self-tender offer.
Plus the tender, can you just address the timing of that?
