On November 2, 2007 Agilysys, Inc. (the "Company") issued a press release announcing a revision to its previously issued results for the fiscal 2008 second quarter ended September 30, 2007. The revision reflects a $5.4 million reclassification of cost of goods sold from product costs to services cost for the three and six months ended September 30, 2007, with no effect to total sales, cost of goods sold or gross margin. The reclassification will be reflected in the Company's Form 10-Q for the period ended September 30, 2007.
