SECTION 7. COLLATERAL
     To secure the prompt payment and performance of all Obligations, each Borrower hereby grants to Agent, for the benefit of Secured Parties, a continuing security interest in and Lien upon all personal Property of such Borrower, including all of the following Property (but specifically excluding Excluded Assets), whether now owned or hereafter acquired, and wherever located:
7.1.
Grant of Security Interest
.
          (a) all Accounts;
          (b) all Chattel Paper, including electronic chattel paper;
