The following information shall not be deemed "filed" for purposes of Section 18 of the Securities Exchange Act of 1934, as amended (the "Exchange Act"), or incorporated by reference in any filing under the Securities Act of 1933, as amended, or the Exchange Act, except as shall be expressly set forth by specific reference in such a filing.
On August 9, 2011, Agilysys, Inc. (the "Company") issued a press release announcing its results for the fiscal 2012 first quarter ended June 30, 2011. A copy of the press release is attached hereto as Exhibit 99.1 and incorporated by reference herein. A copy of the slide presentation for the earnings webcast conference call is also attached hereto as Exhibit 99.2 and incorporated by reference herein.
 
 
