On October 27, 2012, the Board of Directors of Agilysys, Inc. (the "Company") elected Robert R. Ellis, the Company's Senior Vice President, Chief Financial Officer and Treasurer, to the additional office of Chief Operating Officer of the Company. Mr. Ellis, 39, joined the Company in October 2011 as Senior Vice President and Chief Financial Officer. Effective with his new appointment, Mr. Ellis' annual salary will be increased to $300,000, and his fiscal year annual incentive opportunity will be increased to 75% of his base salary.
The Company issued a press release on November 8, 2012 announcing the appointment of Mr. Ellis as Chief Operating Officer, which is furnished as Exhibit 99.1 to this Current Report on Form 8-K.
 
