Contract
 means any written or oral contract, instrument, agreement, commitment, license agreement, lease, obligation, undertaking, sales order (including delivery orders, purchase orders and change orders), joint venture, indenture, or evidence of indebtedness relative to the Business to which the Seller is a party or is otherwise obligated.
