(b)
    
This Agreement and the Related Agreements have been duly executed and delivered by Buyer and, assuming the due execution and delivery of this Agreement, and, as applicable, the Related Agreements, by the Seller, constitute valid and binding obligations of Buyer enforceable in accordance with their terms except as may be limited by applicable bankruptcy, reorganization, insolvency, or moratorium.
