Brokers, Finders
. No finder, broker, agent, or other intermediary acting on behalf of Buyer, directly or indirectly, is entitled to a commission, fee, or other compensation or obligation for which Seller may be liable in connection with the negotiation or consummation of this Agreement or any applicable Related Agreement or any of the transactions contemplated hereby.
